    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, always kept in the garage, and there's not a single scratch or dent to be found. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move quickly. You've seriously got to see this beauty in person to believe how clean it is! \u2728",
